{"title":"油茶树","authors":["萧通湖"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":2,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"油茶树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧通湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湘南的青山，扑面相迎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一坡坡，一棵棵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽是油茶树。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油茶树啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未入群芳谱，鲜见丹青图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎比得岁寒三友："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松梅竹？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"故地相逢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜向绵绵青山索句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人吟松梅竹，我唱油茶树——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吟在葱茏岭壑间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一帧带韵的水墨画。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颤着清露的茶子花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如雪似玉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生苦旅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滋润我纯朴的情愫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无意争春斗艳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乐在收获时节忙花事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对芬芳的明天含笑祝福。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫坡硕果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竞把酽酽秋情吐露，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成熟的笑容，醉倾千山万谷？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那清亮清亮的茶油啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你一脉飘香的心语。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带来赤子挚诚的祝福——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你郁郁葱葱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱心不老，年年富足；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留下一腔美妙的向往——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倘能重生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甘作青山一棵油茶树。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}